After the radiation treatment my dad can't produce much saliva.  It takes him forever to eat and things he used to love to eat taste totally different now.  He constantly has cottenmouth that he can't cure, he can sip some water and kinda get rid of it but it comes back an many other things I won't bore you with.  Now he has to live with the thought that it could come back and he could maybe die.<br>
<br>
Would suck to lose him.  Do yourself and those around you a favor and think twice about dangers in your lifestyle.  Hell, I am only 26 and wish I could go back and do so many things over again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#212141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub114.ezboard.com/utortoiseeldersquirtle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TortoiseEldersquirtle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 96<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/27/02 11:46:24 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3103.topic&index=78>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Um</span><hr size=1> Why are there random flames thrown at me here? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub114.ezboard.com/uctenn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ctenn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_yellowspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/27/02 10:58:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3103.topic&index=79>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> umm</span><hr size=1> omg omg lol lol<br>
