<br>
Uh, weed is natural.  It's a plant. It grows from the soil, is picked, dried, and smoked.  But you're right about one thing, chemicals do suck -- that's why I'd smoke weed anyday over using any pharmaceutical drugs.  Bet you didn't know adverse reactions to pharmaceutical drugs kills over 100,000 people a year and is 4th on the NVSS's leading causes of deaths in the US under 'accidents and adverse reactions', did ya now.<br>
<br>
Know how many die from illegal hardcore drugs? (heroin, coke, crack, amphetamines)  20,000.  Car accidents? 40,000.  Percentage of that 40,000 that was alcohol related deaths?  30%.  <br>
<br>
Deaths from marijuana? 0.  Marijuana-related traffic fatalities? 0.  So again I ask where this '10,000 probable marijuana deaths' comes from, because it sounds like propaganda to me.  Whereas 100,000 deaths, 5 times that of illegal drugs, is a hard number.  Know how many drugs the FDA has recalled since 1993?  2079.  That's TWO THOUSAND+ drugs, and that's only prescription drugs and not including over-the-counter.  Since 1983 they've withdrawn off the market completely almost 3% of all drugs approved...all hard facts from the FDA-run CDER (center for drug evaluation and research).  So keep on spouting your '10,000 <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> probable</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> marijuana deaths' bullshit and attributing congenital birth affects to weed, cause someone somewhere might be dumb enough to believe you.<br>
<br>
As for cancer, the odds on you developing any form of cancer in your lifetime are 1 in 3.  Yes, that's a real statistic...1 in 3.  The best lottery odds you'll ever see.  Everything you do from taking light in through your eyes to eating causes free radicals that can destroy oncogenes and lead to abnormal cell growth.  You could be the healthiest person in the world and deny yourself every little pleasure and still die a horrible organ-liquefying death.  Or you could smoke cigarettes and drink till the day you die and never develop it.  Either way, you might as well enjoy yourself while you're here.<br>
<br>
Toke em if you got em. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showMessageRange?topicID=3103.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showMessageRange?topicID=3103.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showMessageRange?topicID=3103.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b> <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showMessageRange?topicID=3103.topic&start=81&stop=81>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showPrevMessage?topicID=3103.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showNextMessage?topicID=3103.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3103.topic&index=80><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.threadControl?topicID=3103.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3103.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub114.ezboard.com/flegacyofsteel43089general.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3103.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub114.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0"